  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Prospective collection of data of possible prognostic relevance in patients with indolent non
      - follicular B-CELL Lymphomas.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The present study is designed as a prospective collection of information potentially useful
      to predict the prognosis of newly diagnosed patients with non-follicular low grade B-cell
      lymphoma.

      The study is aimed to verify whether a prognostic collection of data would allow the
      development of a more accurate prognostic assessment for non-follicular low grade B-cell
      lymphomas.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
